The paper discusses the use of neural networks for learning independent components, which is a topic related to machine learning and neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also uses mutual information neural estimation (MINE) network, which falls under the category of neural estimation (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper involves optimization techniques, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also uses a differentiable encoder network, which is related to computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper involves information theory, which is related to information theory (cs.IT).
